<paragraph blockId="165.[151,1436,1135,1475]" pageId="165" pageNumber="166">
REMARKS: The earliest mention of 
<taxonomicName authority="Le Peletier &amp; Serville, 1828" authorityName="Le Peletier &amp; Serville" authorityYear="1828" box="[620,1188,1253,1279]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Sphaerophoria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="165" pageNumber="166" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[620,796,1253,1278]" italics="true" pageId="165" pageNumber="166">Sphaerophoria</emphasis>
Le Peletier &amp; Serville, 1828
</taxonomicName>
using the spelling “ 
<emphasis box="[260,421,1292,1317]" italics="true" pageId="165" pageNumber="166">Spaerophoria</emphasis>
” that we have found in this study is in 
<bibRefCitation author="Zetterstedt, J. W." box="[937,1236,1292,1318]" pageId="165" pageNumber="166" pagination="840" refId="ref154597" refString="Zetterstedt, J. W. (1852) Diptera Scandinaviae disposita et descripta. Tomus undecimus. Officina Lundbergiana, Lundae [= Lund]. Pp. 4091 - 4545. [22 April] [Dated from Evenhuis (1997: 840).]" type="journal article" year="1852">Zetterstedt (1852: 4514)</bibRefCitation>
, as an incorrect subsequent spelling. In 
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." box="[530,717,1331,1357]" pageId="165" pageNumber="166" pagination="10" refId="ref144790" refString="Rondani, C. (1856) Dipterologiae italicae prodromus. Vol: I. Genera italica ordinis dipterorum ordinatim disposita et distincta et in familias et stirpes aggregata. A. Stocchi, Parmae [= Parma]. 226 + [2] pp. [10 September] [Dated from advertisement from publisher in Stettiner Entomologische Zeitung.]" type="journal article" year="1856">Rondani (1856)</bibRefCitation>
this is either an incorrect subsequent spelling or unjustified emendation (by virtue of similar spelling changes in two or more names from “ph” to “p” in the same work). We thus follow ICZN 
<emphasis box="[616,678,1410,1435]" italics="true" pageId="165" pageNumber="166">Code</emphasis>
Article 33.5 in treating this spelling in 
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." box="[1172,1360,1410,1436]" pageId="165" pageNumber="166" pagination="10" refId="ref144790" refString="Rondani, C. (1856) Dipterologiae italicae prodromus. Vol: I. Genera italica ordinis dipterorum ordinatim disposita et distincta et in familias et stirpes aggregata. A. Stocchi, Parmae [= Parma]. 226 + [2] pp. [10 September] [Dated from advertisement from publisher in Stettiner Entomologische Zeitung.]" type="journal article" year="1856">Rondani (1856)</bibRefCitation>
as an incorrect subsequent spelling.
</paragraph>
